<%- include('partials/header', {title: 'Adoption Process | Shanti & Bryan Pinscher Kennel'}) %>

<section class="page-section">
  <p class="section-label">How It Works</p>
  <h1>Our Adoption Process</h1>
  <div class="section-underline"></div>
  <p style="margin-top:20px;">Bringing home one of our puppies is a thoughtful, guided journey. Here's exactly what to expect from first contact to take-home day.</p>

  <div class="process-timeline">
    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="process-num">1</div>
      <div class="process-content">
        <div class="process-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-pen"></i></div>
        <h3>Application</h3>
        <p>Begin by reaching out through our contact page and telling us a little about your family, your home, and what you're looking for in a companion. This helps us match you with the right puppy.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="process-num">2</div>
      <div class="process-content">
        <div class="process-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-phone-volume"></i></div>
        <h3>Phone Consultation</h3>
        <p>We'll arrange a friendly conversation to answer your questions, discuss our puppies and upcoming litters, and make sure a Miniature Pinscher is the right fit for your lifestyle.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="process-num">3</div>
      <div class="process-content">
        <div class="process-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-hand-holding-dollar"></i></div>
        <h3>Reservation Deposit</h3>
        <p>Once you've found your perfect match, a deposit reserves your puppy exclusively for you. Your puppy is then marked as Reserved and held just for your family.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="process-num">4</div>
      <div class="process-content">
        <div class="process-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-paw"></i></div>
        <h3>Puppy Selection</h3>
        <p>As your puppy grows, we'll share regular photos and updates. We'll guide you through selection and keep you involved every step as your companion develops.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="process-num">5</div>
      <div class="process-content">
        <div class="process-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-house-chimney-window"></i></div>
        <h3>Take-Home Day</h3>
        <p>The big day! Your puppy goes home fully vet-checked, vaccinated, and with complete documentation, a health guarantee, and our lifelong support as your breeder.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="process-num">6</div>
      <div class="process-content">
        <div class="process-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-truck-fast"></i></div>
        <h3>Delivery or Local Pickup, Your Choice</h3>
        <p>Wherever you are, we'll get your puppy to you. We partner with a trusted, experienced pet transport agency for safe nationwide delivery, so you never have to worry about traveling to us. If you're nearby and would rather meet us in person, local pickup at our home is always welcome too, where you can see firsthand how your puppy was raised.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top:50px;">
    <a href="/puppies" class="btn">View Available Puppies</a>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold" style="margin-left:12px;">Start Your Application</a>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
